    skos:definition "Network Remediation Activity events report on attempts at remediating computer networks. It follows the MITRE countermeasures defined by the D3FEND™ <a target='_blank' href='https://d3fend.mitre.org/'>Matrix</a>. Techniques and Sub-techniques will include Network, such as Network Isolation or Network Traffic Filtering." ;
    skos:inScheme ocsf:events ;
    ocsf:ocsf_event_uid 4 .

