    skos:altLabel "OSINT" ;
    skos:definition "The OSINT (Open Source Intelligence) profile contains one or more indicators and associated analysis and details, such as registrar (WHOIS) information and commentary about a hostname, or information about a digital certificate and its usage within a campaign. This information can be used to further enrich a detection or finding by providing decisioning support to other analysts and engineers within the profile itself." ;
    skos:inScheme ocsf:profiles ;
    ocsf:ocsf_profile "osint" .

