    owl:unionOf ( <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#ADWARE> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#BACKDOOR> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#BOT> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#BOOTKIT> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#DDOS> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#DOWNLOADER> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#DROPPER> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#EXPLOIT_KIT> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#KEYLOGGER> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#RANSOMWARE> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#REMOTE_ACCESS_TROJAN> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#RESOURCE_EXPLOITATION> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#ROGUE_SECURITY_SOFTWARE> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#ROOTKIT> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#SCREEN_CAPTURE> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#SPYWARE> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#TROJAN> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#VIRUS> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#WEBSHELL> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#WIPER> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#WORM> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#UNKNOWN> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/MalwareClassificationIdsEnum#OTHER> ) ;
